    body
      // Header
      header
        .container
            .divider
                .logo
                    a(href="../").logo
                        span Talk Push Logo
                    a(href="#").menu-button
                        i(class="fa fa-bars",aria-hidden="true")
                .menu
                    include ../../jade/_navigation.jade
      
      .display-header.augmented-recruiter
        .filter
          .container
            .augmented-header
              .video
                .video-holder
                  iframe(width='560', height='315', src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/abg2U9DuAiA', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen='')
              .header-text
                h1 Augmented Recruiter
                p Every month, we feature recruiters who embrace automation in our Augmented Recruiters Series.
                p This month we feature Ping Catalina from Alexander Mann Solutions.
      .white-holder.equal.white-theme
        .container
          .augmented-display: img(src="../images/augmented-page/display.jpg", alt="Augmented Recruiter")
          h2.augmented-name 5 Questions about Ping Sta. Catalina
          
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title Hello please tell us about your scope of responsibilities at Alexander Mann Solutions?
          p.augmented-body I am a Client Services Manager functioning in Recruiting for different BPO clients.
          
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title What do you like most working in recruitment?
          p.augmented-body It allows me to develop professional relationships where I learn best practices, be updated with interviewing techniques and latest technologies.
          
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title How has technology changed the way you work since you started out in recruitment?
          p.augmented-body It’s evolved in such a way that recruiting is no longer limited to an 8-hour job. It allowed access to.
          
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title What new hack/tool/technology do you recommend to your fellow “augmented recruiters?
          p.augmented-body I have always recommended Talkpush because it is a non traditional tool that allows us access to several tools in one platform.
          
          hr.augmented-line
          h3.augmented-title Enough about recruitment! What is your favorite science fiction movie of all time?
          p.augmented-body Avatar
          
